PN,44401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775408752
OL,3,CIT system for Northern Ireland schools
OL,4,Ctargeted by cyber attack
OL,6,FAn IT system used by pupils in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland has been hit by a
OL,8,Fcyber attack, the Education Authority
OL,9,F(EA) said.
OL,11,FThe EA said it was taking the incident
OL,12,F"very seriously" and apologised for
OL,13,Fthe impact on pupils who may be
OL,14,Fpreparing for exams over the Easter
OL,15,Fbreak.
OL,17,FA password reset has been issued to
OL,18,Fusers of the C2K school system.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775408752
OL,3,CIT system for Northern Ireland schools
OL,4,Ctargeted by cyber attack
OL,6,FThe EA said it could not yet confirm
OL,7,Fwhether personal data had been
OL,8,Fcompromised and it was engaging with
OL,9,Fthe Information Commissioner's Office.
OL,11,F"We can confirm that the C2K school
OL,12,Fsystem has been the target of a cyber
OL,13,Fattack," an EA spokesman said.
OL,15,F"As soon as we became aware of the
OL,16,Fincident, the system managers, Capita,
OL,17,Ftook immediate steps to contain the
OL,18,Fissue and begin a full investigation.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@HO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775408752
OL,3,CIT system for Northern Ireland schools
OL,4,Ctargeted by cyber attack
OL,6,F"The investigation is at an early
OL,7,Fstage and we are not yet able to
OL,8,Fconfirm whether any personal data has
OL,9,Fbeen affected.
OL,11,F"We are taking this very seriously and
OL,12,Fare engaging with the Information
OL,13,FCommissioner's Office and relevant
OL,14,Fauthorities as part of our response.
OL,16,F"As a critical security measure, a
OL,17,Ffull password reset has been carried
OL,18,Fout across the school network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775408752
OL,3,CIT system for Northern Ireland schools
OL,4,Ctargeted by cyber attack
OL,6,F"Capita is conducting further security
OL,7,Ftests, and access to the system is
OL,8,Fcurrently unavailable.
OL,10,F"We will update users on the
OL,11,Farrangements for regaining access as
OL,12,Fsoon as possible, including
OL,13,Farrangements for password resets.
OL,15,F"These steps are essential in the
OL,16,Fcontext of maintaining the integrity
OL,17,Fand security of the system and the
OL,18,Fsafety of all users.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775408752
OL,3,CIT system for Northern Ireland schools
OL,4,Ctargeted by cyber attack
OL,6,F"We understand and sincerely apologise
OL,7,Ffor the impact on staff and pupils;
OL,8,Fparticularly pupils who may be
OL,9,Fpreparing for exams or completing
OL,10,Fcoursework during the Easter period.
OL,12,F"We are working hard to resolve this
OL,13,Fproblem as soon as possible."
